(66, 'd', '', '<div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Oxygen, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.35px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); letter-spacing: normal;">To switch fromÂ <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 1px 5px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px;">php 5.6</code>Â toÂ <code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 1px 5px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px;">php 7.0</code>Â you need to do two things:</p><pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 5px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.57143; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(234, 238, 240); border: 0px; border-radius: 4px; width: auto; max-height: 600px;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; border: 0px;"># For php in web apps\r\nsudo a2dismod php5.6 && sudo a2enmod php7.0 && sudo service apache2 restart\r\n# For php-cli in the command line\r\nsudo ln -sfn /usr/bin/php7.0 /etc/alternatives/php\r\n</code></pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); letter-spacing: normal;">or from php7.0 to php5.6:</p><pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 5px; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.57143; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(234, 238, 240); border: 0px; border-radius: 4px; width: auto; max-height: 600px;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; border: 0px;"># For php in web apps\r\nsudo a2dismod php7.0 && sudo a2enmod php5.6 && sudo service apache2 restart\r\n# For php-cli in the command line\r\nsudo ln -sfn /usr/bin/php5.6 /etc/alternatives/php\r\n</code></pre></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Oxygen, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.35px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></div><br class="Apple-interchange-newline">', ',,,,,,,,,dfdfdsf,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,sdfdsfsdf,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,df', 0, '', 1, 1, '2016-12-05 11:42:05', '2016-12-13 07:14:43', 6, '5', '0000-00-00', NULL, 0),
